<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA45">
<l>āmē yamarark kaṟiya vatuniṟka</l>
<l>nāmē yaṟikiṟpō naṉṉeñcē – pūmēya</l>
<l>mātavattōṉ ṟāḷpaṇinta vāḷarakka ṉīṇmuṭiyaip</l>
<l>pātamattā leṇṇiṉāṉ paṇpu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There are things not known to the immortals. Let that rest.</l>
<l>We, we can know [them], good heart – [those] qualities of the one who counted</l>
<l>with [his] feet the tall heads of the Rākṣasa with a sword  who had humbled</l>
<l>himself at the feet of the one with great penance who resides in the flower.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
